    maBooking ID #REQUIRED
    maTour IDREF #REQUIRED
    maKhachHang IDREF #REQUIRED>

<!ELEMENT thoiGianDat (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT trangThai (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT soTien (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT phuongThucThanhToan (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT diemDanhGia (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT noiDungDanhGia (#PCDATA)>

